    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Automated FEA Strength Verification of Bolted Joints</h1>\n<p>Developed a <strong>14-step automated ABAQUS Python workflow</strong> for the verification of safety-critical bolted joints in Electronic Power Steering (EPS) systems.</p>\n<p>✔ <strong>90% reduction</strong> in manual verification time<br>\n✔ <strong>&#x3C;0.5% deviation</strong> from physical tests<br>\n✔ <strong>100% conservative</strong> design validation<br>\n✔ Enabled faster design iterations for production systems</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/portfolio/static/19ce669b4e3b2665b95108c417194732/4466a/steering.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 77.71428571428571%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Architectural Components of the EPS Steering Assembly\"\n        title=\"Architectural Components of the EPS Steering Assembly\"\n        src=\"/portfolio/static/19ce669b4e3b2665b95108c417194732/39600/steering.png\"\n        srcset=\"/portfolio/static/19ce669b4e3b2665b95108c417194732/1aaec/steering.png 175w,\n/portfolio/static/19ce669b4e3b2665b95108c417194732/98287/steering.png 350w,\n/portfolio/static/19ce669b4e3b2665b95108c417194732/39600/steering.png 700w,\n/portfolio/static/19ce669b4e3b2665b95108c417194732/57cd1/steering.png 1050w,\n/portfolio/static/19ce669b4e3b2665b95108c417194732/4af54/steering.png 1400w,\n/portfolio/static/19ce669b4e3b2665b95108c417194732/4466a/steering.png 1740w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 1: Identification of critical bolted joint locations in steering housing assemblies</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Project Overview</h2>\n<p>Bolted joints in <strong>Electronic Power Steering (EPS)</strong> systems are safety-critical and experience complex dynamic loads. Traditional <strong>VDI 2230</strong> calculations rely on simplified assumptions and are difficult to scale for complex geometries.</p>\n<p>This project modernized the verification process by combining <strong>high-fidelity finite element analysis</strong>, <strong>automated post-processing</strong>, and <strong>custom ABAQUS plug-in development</strong> to create a scalable and validated workflow.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Automation Workflow</h2>\n<p>The core of this project was the development of a custom <strong>ABAQUS Plug-In</strong> using the <strong>Python API</strong>.</p>\n<p>The workflow automates a rigorous <strong>14-step engineering pipeline</strong>, ensuring consistency across design iterations:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Multi-Model Transition</strong><br>\nTransition from high-complexity <strong>Model Class III</strong> to simplified <strong>Model Class I</strong> for standardized verification.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Load Case Automation</strong><br>\nIntegrated handling of preload, thermal effects, and operational loads into a unified workflow.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Automated Verification Logic</strong><br>\nAutomatic extraction of history and field outputs for:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Working stress</li>\n<li>Assembly stress</li>\n<li>Minimum length of engagement</li>\n<li>Pull-out safety verification</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/portfolio/static/1f0bc98b04c5c5d09e05e86ff9003248/baba4/fc2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 118.85714285714286%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"The 14-Step Automated Verification Pipeline\"\n        title=\"The 14-Step Automated Verification Pipeline\"\n        src=\"/portfolio/static/1f0bc98b04c5c5d09e05e86ff9003248/39600/fc2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/portfolio/static/1f0bc98b04c5c5d09e05e86ff9003248/1aaec/fc2.png 175w,\n/portfolio/static/1f0bc98b04c5c5d09e05e86ff9003248/98287/fc2.png 350w,\n/portfolio/static/1f0bc98b04c5c5d09e05e86ff9003248/39600/fc2.png 700w,\n/portfolio/static/1f0bc98b04c5c5d09e05e86ff9003248/57cd1/fc2.png 1050w,\n/portfolio/static/1f0bc98b04c5c5d09e05e86ff9003248/baba4/fc2.png 1346w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 2: Workflow logic for the ABAQUS automation plug-in</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Validation &#x26; Correlation</h2>\n<p>The automated workflow was benchmarked against classical <strong>VDI 2230</strong> analytical calculations using a connecting rod test case.</p>\n<p>The results demonstrated near-perfect correlation, validating the script’s ability to replace manual calculations for complex parts.</p>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto; margin: 3em 0;\">\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; table-layout: fixed; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.95em;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: var(--light-navy); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green);\">\n        <th style=\"width: 40%; text-align: left; padding: 20px; color: var(--green);\">Quantity</th>\n        <th style=\"width: 20%; text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: var(--green);\">VDI 2230</th>\n        <th style=\"width: 20%; text-align: center; padding: 20px;\">FEM Script</th>\n        <th style=\"width: 20%; text-align: right; padding: 20px;\">Difference</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--lightest-navy);\">\n        <td style=\"text-align: left; padding: 20px;\">Min required clamp load</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: center; padding: 20px;\">16267 N</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: center; padding: 20px;\">16155 N</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: right; padding: 20px; color: var(--green);\"><strong>-0.69%</strong></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--lightest-navy);\">\n        <td style=\"text-align: left; padding: 20px;\">Embedding loss</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: center; padding: 20px;\">1103 N</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: center; padding: 20px;\">1101 N</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: right; padding: 20px; color: var(--green);\"><strong>-0.20%</strong></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"text-align: left; padding: 20px;\">Safety margin</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: center; padding: 20px;\">1.43</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: center; padding: 20px;\">1.42</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: right; padding: 20px; color: var(--green);\"><strong>+0.70%</strong></td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/portfolio/static/8318b0df23053f3d1e7ac73b09fc0e2e/1d4c8/pull.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.857142857142854%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Experimental Pull-Out Test vs. Simulation Model\"\n        title=\"Experimental Pull-Out Test vs. Simulation Model\"\n        src=\"/portfolio/static/8318b0df23053f3d1e7ac73b09fc0e2e/39600/pull.png\"\n        srcset=\"/portfolio/static/8318b0df23053f3d1e7ac73b09fc0e2e/1aaec/pull.png 175w,\n/portfolio/static/8318b0df23053f3d1e7ac73b09fc0e2e/98287/pull.png 350w,\n/portfolio/static/8318b0df23053f3d1e7ac73b09fc0e2e/39600/pull.png 700w,\n/portfolio/static/8318b0df23053f3d1e7ac73b09fc0e2e/57cd1/pull.png 1050w,\n/portfolio/static/8318b0df23053f3d1e7ac73b09fc0e2e/4af54/pull.png 1400w,\n/portfolio/static/8318b0df23053f3d1e7ac73b09fc0e2e/1d4c8/pull.png 1412w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 3: Experimental validation through pull-out testing</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Fail-Safe Material Model Calibration</h2>\n<p>A critical finding of the research addressed the <strong>non-conservative behavior</strong> of <strong>AlSi12 aluminum alloys</strong> in stripping failure calculations.</p>\n<p>To ensure fail-safe design, experimental results were used to derive a hardness-based shear limit relation:</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><strong>τ<sub>B</sub> / HB = 1.5</strong></p>\n<p>By integrating this into the verification logic, the workflow achieved:</p>\n<p>✔ <strong>100% conservativeness</strong><br>\n✔ Reliable lower-bound structural integrity prediction<br>\n✔ Improved confidence for mass-production steering assemblies</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/portfolio/static/9a557a3cfc0152b92cb613a54354747a/5d78e/p1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.285714285714285%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Stress Gradient Comparison at Failure Limits\"\n        title=\"Stress Gradient Comparison at Failure Limits\"\n        src=\"/portfolio/static/9a557a3cfc0152b92cb613a54354747a/39600/p1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/portfolio/static/9a557a3cfc0152b92cb613a54354747a/1aaec/p1.png 175w,\n/portfolio/static/9a557a3cfc0152b92cb613a54354747a/98287/p1.png 350w,\n/portfolio/static/9a557a3cfc0152b92cb613a54354747a/39600/p1.png 700w,\n/portfolio/static/9a557a3cfc0152b92cb613a54354747a/57cd1/p1.png 1050w,\n/portfolio/static/9a557a3cfc0152b92cb613a54354747a/4af54/p1.png 1400w,\n/portfolio/static/9a557a3cfc0152b92cb613a54354747a/5d78e/p1.png 2466w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 4: FEM and experimental comparison for conservative failure prediction</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Engineering Insights</h2>\n<p>The project also provided detailed insights into local stress distributions and thread engagement behavior.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/portfolio/static/b6ce2a752dde342e7047aaa1dffd5a6d/c3381/p2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.142857142857146%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Thread Stress Distribution and Failure Zones\"\n        title=\"Thread Stress Distribution and Failure Zones\"\n        src=\"/portfolio/static/b6ce2a752dde342e7047aaa1dffd5a6d/39600/p2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/portfolio/static/b6ce2a752dde342e7047aaa1dffd5a6d/1aaec/p2.png 175w,\n/portfolio/static/b6ce2a752dde342e7047aaa1dffd5a6d/98287/p2.png 350w,\n/portfolio/static/b6ce2a752dde342e7047aaa1dffd5a6d/39600/p2.png 700w,\n/portfolio/static/b6ce2a752dde342e7047aaa1dffd5a6d/57cd1/p2.png 1050w,\n/portfolio/static/b6ce2a752dde342e7047aaa1dffd5a6d/4af54/p2.png 1400w,\n/portfolio/static/b6ce2a752dde342e7047aaa1dffd5a6d/c3381/p2.png 1876w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 5: Thread stress distribution and identification of critical zones</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Key Takeaway</h2>\n<p>This project transformed a manual, approximation-based engineering verification process into a <strong>scalable</strong>, <strong>validated</strong>, and <strong>production-ready automation workflow</strong> for safety-critical automotive applications.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Automated FEA Strength Verification of Bolted Joints","description":"Developed a 14-step ABAQUS Python workflow to automate the verification of safety-critical bolted joints in EPS systems.","date":"2021-06","slug":"/featured/bolt-analysis","tags":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/featured/bolt-analysis"}},
